<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard Penjualan - MBP</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    
    <style>
        /* ==================== CETAKAN STRUKTUR WAJIB KONSISTEN ==================== */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f6; display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }
        
        .main-content {
            margin-left: 260px; /* Mengunci jarak agar pas dengan lebar sidebar */
            padding: 40px;
            width: calc(100% - 260px);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .topbar { 
            display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center; 
            margin-bottom: 30px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .admin-profile { 
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; background: white; 
            padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; 
            font-weight: 600; color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }
        .admin-profile i { color: #03ac0e; font-size: 18px; }
        /* ========================================================================== */

        /* Style unik halaman Dashboard */
        .welcome-banner { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #f0fdf4 100%); 
            border: 1px solid #dcfce7; border-left: 5px solid #03ac0e; border-radius: 16px; 
            padding: 35px 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(3, 172, 14, 0.05); 
        }
        .welcome-banner h2 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: #14532d; }
        .welcome-banner p { margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; }

        .grid-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; }
        .action-card { 
            background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 25px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; 
            text-decoration: none; color: #1e293b; transition: 0.2s ease; 
        }
        .action-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #03ac0e; box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(3, 172, 14, 0.08); }
        .action-icon { width: 55px; height: 55px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 24px; }
        .bg-green { background: #dcfce7; color: #16a34a; }
        .bg-blue { background: #e0f2fe; color: #0284c7; }
        .bg-orange { background: #ffedd5; color: #ea580c; }
        .action-text h4 { margin: 0 0 4px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; }
        .action-text p { margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('../partials/sidebar', { role: role }) %>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="topbar">
            <div class="admin-profile">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle"></i>
                <%= typeof namaUser !== 'undefined' ? namaUser : 'Tim Penjualan' %>
                <span style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; margin-left: 5px;">Penjualan</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="welcome-banner">
            <h2>Dashboard Penjualan</h2>
            <p>Selamat datang di panel pengelolaan transaksi PT Mitrabeton Perkasa.<br>Pantau pesanan masuk dan pastikan operasional pemesanan pelanggan berjalan lancar hari ini.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 20px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Menu Operasional</h3>
        
        <div class="grid-cards">
            <a href="/penjualan/pesanan" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon bg-orange"><i class="bi bi-cart-check-fill"></i></div>
                <div class="action-text">
                    <h4>Verifikasi Pesanan</h4>
                    <p>Kelola pesanan masuk & pembayaran</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/penjualan/produk" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon bg-green"><i class="bi bi-box-seam-fill"></i></div>
                <div class="action-text">
                    <h4>Katalog Produk</h4>
                    <p>Tambah dan ubah harga beton/alat</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/penjualan/kategori" class="action-card">
                <div class="action-icon bg-blue"><i class="bi bi-tags-fill"></i></div>
                <div class="action-text">
                    <h4>Kategori</h4>
                    <p>Kelola jenis dan mutu beton</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>